fulltitle: Doc Cheatham Interview by Monk Rowe and  Michael Woods - 7/28/95 - NYC
title: Doc Cheatham Interview by Monk Rowe and  Michael Woods - 7/28/95 - NYC
description:
Trumpeter Doc Cheatham reminisces about subbing for Louis Armstrong, working with Benny Goodman,  participating in some of the earliest jazz recordings, and working with Latin bands.
